KAWAIIKAWAIIFAAAAIIRRR🐻🍡

- Dubfit.. New era “Cutie Suika” putting things in its place in the Luv Rated game.

So I had decided that I couldn’t keep going with the whole leaving kids I had made behind so I put up a post on DeviantArt about a time I had recently remembered and I got the most beautiful response…

So I’ve decided to memorialize a young 14 year old (with looks of a 11 year old) girl named Cutie Suika and have continued on from the story I left off with.

Going off the dialogue here and promises acceptance of the headcanon, I recognize all of the subjects as canon to my headcanon except for Mr. Liemas. I have always seen him as a child, or maybe a toddler myself, and I have never seen him as any older or younger.

This was the first time someone has confirmed they actively used my headcanon and I’m so glad!

So after this encounter I decided to use posterized pictures of my children pictured to make this cute comic (and to do my first comic by hand no less).

All my characters are:

Cutie Suika - an officially claimed previously thought unwanted
